<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/jan/17/">&#x27a0;</a> January 17, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="privatecopy-epetition-reply" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.pm.gov.uk/output/Page10776.asp">privatecopy - epetition reply</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The UK goverment has started posting public responses to petitions filed using their &#8220;Petition the Prime Minister&#8221; site.   They&#8217;re mostly your standard &#8220;don&#8217;t worry your sweet head&#8221; brush-off you&#8217;d get from writing to your MP, but it&#8217;s good to see, nonetheless.</p>

