<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/oct/22/">&#x27a0;</a> October 22, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="walk_it_a_step" >

        
        <a name="003015"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.walkit.com/index.aspx">Walk It - A step in the right direction</a></h4>

        

        <p>Site which gives you walking directions around London.  Since most major cities have wacky one-way restrictions, driving directions are rarely handy.  I&#8217;m surprised Google Maps et al don&#8217;t support this kind of thing.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
