<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jun/29/">&#x27a0;</a> June 29, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="bbc_news_have_y" >

        
        <a name="002640"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://newsforums.bbc.co.uk/nol/thread.jspa?threadID=2354&amp;&amp;edition=1&amp;ttl=20060629204809">BBC NEWS | Have Your Say: Where next for national identity?</a></h4>

        

        <p>Fascinating bitchfest on the BBC discussion site around Scottish folks not supporting England in international sporting events.  Interestingly, most of the kneejerk racist comments are from the English, accusing Scots, amongst other things, of being &#8220;bitter miserable idiots&#8221;.</p>

